PN,38301
SC,0001
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F383A1777025179
OL,3,CConcerns raised over how Guernsey
OL,4,Cdoctors are regulated by one of their
OL,5,Cown
OL,7,FA politician in Guernsey has been
OL,8,Ftrying to tease out more information
OL,9,Fabout a role in Guernsey medicine that
OL,10,Fhe says is 'opaque'.
OL,12,FThe island's Responsible Officer
OL,13,Foversees clinical governance and the
OL,14,Frevalidation of doctors.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G1/13
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,384,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38302
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F383A1777025179
OL,3,CConcerns raised over how Guernsey
OL,4,Cdoctors are regulated by one of their
OL,5,Cown
OL,7,FDeputy Gavin St Pier thinks there
OL,8,Fshould be more scrutiny of the role,
OL,9,Fand has raised a myriad of concerns
OL,10,Fincluding 'conflicts of interest' and
OL,11,Fa 'lack of transparency' during a
OL,12,FStates debate this morning (Thursday
OL,13,F23 April).
OL,15,FEvery year a Responsible Officer's
OL,16,Freport is published, identifying the
OL,17,Fwork done overseeing doctors
OL,18,Fregistered in the island. If concerns
OL,19,Fare raised about a doctor, and an
OL,20,Finvestigation launched some of those
OL,21,Fdetails will be in this report.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G2/13
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,384,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38303
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F383A1777025179
OL,3,CConcerns raised over how Guernsey
OL,4,Cdoctors are regulated by one of their
OL,5,Cown
OL,7,FIt is not usually debated, just waved
OL,8,Fthrough. But Deputy St Pier has a
OL,9,Frecord of getting this in front of the
OL,10,FStates for debate.
OL,12,FInfamously in 2022 he used this as an
OL,13,Fopportunity to name a local doctor,
OL,14,Fwhich then led to four code of conduct
OL,15,Finvestigations, one abuse of privilege
OL,16,Fcomplaint, a further complaint to HSC,
OL,17,Fand two arrests.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G3/13
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,384,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38304
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F383A1777025179
OL,3,CConcerns raised over how Guernsey
OL,4,Cdoctors are regulated by one of their
OL,5,Cown
OL,7,FThis time his focus was on the
OL,8,FResponsible Officer himself - Dr Peter
OL,9,FRabey. But he was shut down and told
OL,10,Fthat the debate could only be on the
OL,11,Fcontent of the report.
OL,13,FIn an interview with ITV News Deputy
OL,14,FGavin St Pier revealed what he could
OL,15,Fnot say in the States debate:
OL,17,F"I think this is the only opportunity
OL,18,Fin the year to talk about the
OL,19,Fregulation of the health care sector
OL,20,Fand clearly arguably one of our most
OL,21,Fimportant public services.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G4/13
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,384,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38305
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F383A1777025179
OL,3,CConcerns raised over how Guernsey
OL,4,Cdoctors are regulated by one of their
OL,5,Cown
OL,7,F"I think to try and narrow the debate
OL,8,Fpurely to the contents of the report
OL,9,Frestricted it far too much as opposed
OL,10,Fto the law around which the report is
OL,11,Fstructured, which is clearly where I
OL,12,Fwas seeking to take debate.
OL,14,FHe added: "I think it's just it just
OL,15,Fmakes Health and Social Care sound
OL,16,Fvery defensive around all of this,
OL,17,Fwhich I just think is a shame and is
OL,18,Funnecessary.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G5/13
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,384,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38306
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F383A1777025179
OL,3,CConcerns raised over how Guernsey
OL,4,Cdoctors are regulated by one of their
OL,5,Cown
OL,7,F"I didn't really know until really
OL,8,Fvery recently that through the ten
OL,9,Fyears that the Responsible Officer has
OL,10,Fbeen in that role, he's been doing one
OL,11,Fday a week, as a consultant
OL,12,Fanaesthetist - so working with
OL,13,Fsurgeons that he is also responsible
OL,14,Ffor regulating. And, there I think
OL,15,Fthat's one issue.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G6/13
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,384,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38307
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F383A1777025179
OL,3,CConcerns raised over how Guernsey
OL,4,Cdoctors are regulated by one of their
OL,5,Cown
OL,7,F"When it comes to governance and
OL,8,Fconflicts of interests it's very much
OL,9,Fabout perception. Does it pass the
OL,10,Fsmell test? Does it feel right? What
OL,11,Fwould the reasonable person standing
OL,12,Fon the outside think?
OL,14,FDeputy St Pier says he hopes that this
OL,15,Ftime next year his points will be
OL,16,Ftaken on board and the 2026 annual
OL,17,Freport will "perhaps have a bit more
OL,18,Fcolour in it."
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G7/13
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,384,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38308
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F383A1777025179
OL,3,CConcerns raised over how Guernsey
OL,4,Cdoctors are regulated by one of their
OL,5,Cown
OL,7,FDr Peter Rabey, who is the current
OL,8,FResponsible Officer, was not on island
OL,9,Ftoday (Thursday 23 April) and was
OL,10,Funaware of the contents of Deputy St
OL,11,FPier's speech.
OL,13,FITV News have contacted to him, but
OL,14,Fhave not yet had a response.
OL,16,FThe President of Health and Social
OL,17,FCare, Deputy George Oswald, did
OL,18,Fcomment on the debate and said:
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G8/13
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,384,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38309
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F383A1777025179
OL,3,CConcerns raised over how Guernsey
OL,4,Cdoctors are regulated by one of their
OL,5,Cown
OL,7,F"Only in Guernsey does the Responsible
OL,8,FOfficer have to submit an annual
OL,9,Freport to the HSC and through them to
OL,10,Fthe states for debate.
OL,12,F"It would be wrong to place on any
OL,13,Ffuture Responsible Officer further
OL,14,Fpolitical oversight over and above
OL,15,Fthat which already applies locally and
OL,16,Fto doctors fulfilling similar roles in
OL,17,Fother parts of the UK.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G9/13
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,384,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38310
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F383A1777025179
OL,3,CConcerns raised over how Guernsey
OL,4,Cdoctors are regulated by one of their
OL,5,Cown
OL,7,FHe added: "I have regular meetings
OL,8,Fwith Deputy St Pier which cover a
OL,9,Fvariety of matters, much of which may
OL,10,Fbe financial but some which may be
OL,11,Fregulatory. And we have had some
OL,12,Fdiscussion about these matters, and
OL,13,FI'm more than happy to discuss this
OL,14,Ffurther with either himself or other
OL,15,Fmembers.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws        G10/13
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,384,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38311
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F383A1777025179
OL,3,CConcerns raised over how Guernsey
OL,4,Cdoctors are regulated by one of their
OL,5,Cown
OL,7,FDeputy Oswald says he is satisfied
OL,8,Fthat the Responsible Officer's Annual
OL,9,FReport for 2025 provided assurance
OL,10,Fthat the statutory framework for
OL,11,Fmedical regulation "continues to
OL,12,Foperate effectively".
OL,14,FHe added: "The systems of appraisal,
OL,15,Frevalidation, and escalation to the
OL,16,FGeneral Medical Council are clearly
OL,17,Ffunctioning as intended, with a strong
OL,18,Fculture of professional engagement and
OL,19,Foversight.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws        G11/13
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,384,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38312
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F383A1777025179
OL,3,CConcerns raised over how Guernsey
OL,4,Cdoctors are regulated by one of their
OL,5,Cown
OL,7,F"The role of the Responsible Officer
OL,8,Fis central in providing independent
OL,9,Fassurance that concerns are identified
OL,10,Fearly and addressed appropriately.
OL,12,F"While no system can be entirely
OL,13,Fwithout risk, the evidence presented
OL,14,Fin the annual report demonstrates that
OL,15,Fappropriate safeguards are in place
OL,16,Fand are being applied consistently."
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws        G12/13
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
